      <section class="- topic/section ">
         <ol class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">System (PRS or FSC) issue has been assessed and reference material is used by PNL to go over first tier of the troubleshooting. </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">PNL uses the Manufacturing DB to initiate escalation process and involves Discipline Network Leader.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">DNL takes and maintains ownership of the incident, verifies all technical review done by the plant. Updates the incident information, as needed.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">DNL works with Global Network / other DNLs to brainstorm the issue.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">DNL coordinates technical reviews with GNL and R&amp;D until achieving final resolution.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">DNL clearly explains the resolution and closes the service request.</li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">A visual representation of this process can be found in the flowchart in the <xref href="FES-02-100_appendix_%E2%80%93_flowchart_showing_the_support_escalation_procedure_for_fsc_and_prs.dita"
                     class="- topic/xref ">Appendix</xref>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </section>
